WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:02.798
Buy versus build is a tough decision.

00:00:02.798 --> 00:00:05.712
Sapersky however, describes a third way.

00:00:05.712 --> 00:00:09.490
Using third-party components that you can customize during assembly.

00:00:09.490 --> 00:00:13.550
In general with components, you get the risk and cost reduction benefits of

00:00:13.550 --> 00:00:17.260
the buy solution while enjoying the flexibility of the build solution

